en Bass and Olympic gymnast Simone Biles, Cruise rode through Paris, passing by various US Olympians. The flag was carried through the city, eventually reaching a beach party where famous LA musicians performed. The Magnolia star surprised everyone by wrapping up the Paris Olympics and passing the torch to LA, which is going to host the next Summer Games.  Also read:Bluetooth earring company responds to Kamala Harris's debate allegations; offers Trump to\\u2026  \\\"We are like, 'Well, there is no way we are getting this. We are going to get four hours of filming time. We will do the thing,\\\" Wasserman added in his statement to HR displaying his shock and happiness over Cruise's involvement. with the Hollywood sign, he will hand the thing off and he's done. Maybe we will get the other stuff, and the rest will be just a stunt double,\\\" he recalled, \\\"about five minutes into the presentation, [Cruise] goes, 'I am in. But I am only doing it if I get to do everything.\\\"  The Top Gun star who was a regular to the Olympics this season and even watched Simone Biles compete, dazzled everyone with his performance at the closing ceremony on August 11.    \"}"